{"tid":587984,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人試過明知成功機會好低 仍然去表白","createTime":"2018-03-11T01:03:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-18T11:21:55.000Z","uid":152714,"like":83,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":55,"replies":[{"pid":"815061cd9ab081102f40b5af6ffa9ff66cf81a08","tid":587984,"uid":152714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T01:03:22.000Z","msg":"鍾意咗個女同事 <br />\n不過覺得自己 條件差 佢好大機會拒絕我<br />\n<br />\n雖然係咁 但係我真係好想比佢知道我嘅心意<br />\n就算比人拒絕 都叫有似樣嘅結束<br />\n死心都死得徹底啲 <br />\n等自己快啲抽離 專注返自己人生<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae14b0540a4f4a6bfe2f7e5663319d68974fe079","tid":587984,"uid":7954,"like":114,"dislike":0,"score":114,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T01:14:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c959f5ef694b66b222190345935056eb44d17d6f","tid":587984,"uid":170254,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"ae14b0540a4f4a6bfe2f7e5663319d68974fe079","tid":587984,"uid":7954,"like":114,"dislike":0,"score":114,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T01:14:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T01:25:51.000Z","msg":"讚成.....至少另到自己無悔先至最重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04d3ee2ffd15b0acdf5253bb44e123b2633371b3","tid":587984,"uid":152714,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T01:43:03.000Z","msg":"其實我手鏈都買咗 我都唔知點解自己咁痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同佢嘅關係 其實都只係同事關係 <br />\n只係工作上接觸 <br />\n如果衰咗 我又唔怕太尷尬 <br />\n反而尷尬係依家咁<br />\n<br />\n之前同佢相處都無嘜嘢 但係一挑起咗條根 <br />\n搞到我又唔敢直望佢 但係又偷望佢咁 古古怪怪<br />\n可能佢都開始feel到我對佢有啲嘢<br />\n告白咗 我可以放低呢嚿石 做返正常自己<br />\n<br />\n雖然唔知佢點諗 但係如果佢拒絕我 <br />\n我應該都唔會再煩住佢 <br />\n佢應該唔會覺得太困擾吧？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22dcc60ec51ba29e4cd241cab4a78ac1fbd7e1bb","tid":587984,"uid":157579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T01:46:35.000Z","msg":"我依家都係兩頭唔到岸<br />\n諗緊咩時候take action <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9d88107a786ade20d723e3bd61df4cc7355b1f4","tid":587984,"uid":19402,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T01:46:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b2846c86d23f094ed1fb3a7583dbc70e6c29eb3","tid":587984,"uid":78971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T01:51:46.000Z","msg":"拒絕咗咪好尷尬？<br />\n同事喎"},{"pid":"4c043dc90b88c5a11e4d08684dde2b6a3d0edd21","tid":587984,"uid":169676,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"ae14b0540a4f4a6bfe2f7e5663319d68974fe079","tid":587984,"uid":7954,"like":114,"dislike":0,"score":114,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T01:14:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T01:56:41.000Z","msg":"呢啲根本話唔埋<br />\n就算關係好<br />\n都只可能係自作多情一相情願嘅諗法嚟<br />\n以為人地真係啱feel<br />\n其實人地當自己係親密嘅朋友<br />\n而自己走去表白<br />\n一樣都有機會失敗<br />\n<br />\n就算過程中唔表白玩進一步曖昧<br />\n攬下錫下<br />\n但係點知對方係未真係可以接受<br />\n或者一攬一錫完之後嚇到對方走咗呢？<br />\n咁同表白有乜分別？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d3a6f5bb676187ff791af4a1659c19c1652b9c6","tid":587984,"uid":7954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T01:58:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6f2d993999550d90489cc288c738f36d0cf90438","tid":587984,"uid":56219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T01:58:25.000Z","msg":"表白完拒絕面阻阻仲死"},{"pid":"aa7a1b22bf041ff437b0db5ea82bd8f2159a021c","tid":587984,"uid":130901,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T02:00:58.000Z","msg":"表白用黎令自己死心都唔錯, 之後記得扮大方D"},{"pid":"ce2c6359f7752beb94f2cb468fb9987e7005cded","tid":587984,"uid":152714,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T03:10:43.000Z","msg":"我自己覺得大家成年人  廿幾歲 <br />\n應該識handle <br />\n<br />\n我表白