然係同事 <br />\n不過可以話係唔同department 佢係隔離office<br />\n唔係朝見晚見嗰種"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T03:18:10.000Z","msg":"係成年人嘅就諗下人哋感受啦<br />\n你話「唔得嘅，咪以後淨係做野囉」<br />\n你得唔得先？<br />\n真係絲毫尷尬都唔會？<br />\n你做到咁人哋呢？<br />\n如果你自己都覺得機會微嘅，不如做住朋友了解多啲先啦，咁先係負責任嘅表現"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T03:30:01.000Z","msg":"其實我就係諗呢個問題<br />\n<br />\n但係如果淨係講自己 <br />\n我覺得自己可以放得低<br />\n佢就唔知做唔做到<br />\n<br />\n唉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔通 <br />\n真係應該慢慢走入人哋圈子 <br />\n慢慢刷好感度？<br />\n<br />\n但係男人老狗 係咁約女仔去行街睇戲食飯<br />\n目的好明顯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc114b2cf2d6340d09350ecde683ebfbcbed881b","tid":587984,"uid":146893,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T03:38:32.000Z","msg":"點都有機會後悔架喎<br />\n<br />\n後悔同佢表白，最後Friend都無得做<br />\n後悔無去同佢表白<br />\n<br />\n不過老實講，唔試過又真係唔知<br />\n但可以去試探下先囉<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我做緊樣成功機會可能比你更低嘅野"},{"pid":"70be186d2d2abe5cfb92d4828c5a064525b55a6d","tid":587984,"uid":118240,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T03:48:13.000Z","msg":"試過<br />\n本身都知同佢既溝通冇乜化學作用，一定唔會成功<br />\n但只係想佢知道我想佢幸福，並且想幸福既事發生係佢身上，冇論最後果個是否我<br />\n同佢仲 fd，今晚約左食飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76fccdeb83ddaa44a907b0381e273d205d2e18be","tid":587984,"uid":155620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"815061cd9ab081102f40b5af6ffa9ff66cf81a08","tid":587984,"uid":152714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T01:03:22.000Z","msg":"鍾意咗個女同事 <br />\n不過覺得自己 條件差 佢好大機會拒絕我<br />\n<br />\n雖然係咁 但係我真係好想比佢知道我嘅心意<br />\n就算比人拒絕 都叫有似樣嘅結束<br />\n死心都死得徹底啲 <br />\n等自己快啲抽離 專注返自己人生<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T03:49:35.000Z","msg":"只要和你在一起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f7234a876f8c8fa67e8c5d06735157ab8b3102b","tid":587984,"uid":30374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T03:52:40.000Z","msg":"重來都只有因為冇做而後悔<br />\n唔會因爲做咗而後悔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申：All i咗左仲要自己親手整禮物"},{"pid":"a418c5147a60f7e7352142c559af721c577ab6c9","tid":587984,"uid":32938,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T03:53:03.000Z","msg":"起馬拎whatsapp傾下計先 無啦啦自殺式表白<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8969518ce2085f5685bf73ad8b9375904c4aeea","tid":587984,"uid":30374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T03:53:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>重來都只有因為冇做而後悔<br />\n唔會因爲做咗而後悔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申：All <span style=\"color: red;\">in</span>咗左仲要自己親手整禮物</blockquote>"},{"pid":"1d62e093b9df70f3df7b0497e8d21b4b2a9ee88e","tid":587984,"uid":55897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T03:55:53.000Z","msg":"衰在要辭職...講真"},{"pid":"a1c35c00f17e3ad2c11dfa206d40bd0cd25e0dfa","tid":587984,"uid":18607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T03:56:29.000Z","msg":"同事就唔好表白"},{"pid":"3b1c9b58996d5cbf3b367293bce1c525c01d377f","tid":587984,"uid":18607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"815061cd9ab081102f40b5af6ffa9ff66cf81a08","tid":587984,"uid":152714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T01:03:22.000Z","msg":"鍾意咗個女同事 <br />\n不過覺得自己 條件差 佢好大機會拒絕我<br />\n<br />\n雖然係咁 但係我真係好想比佢知道我嘅心意<br />\n就算比人拒絕 都叫有似樣嘅結束<br />\n死心都死得徹底啲 <br />\n等自己快啲抽離 專注返自己人生<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T03:57:31.000Z","msg":"俾啲自信，連自己都覺得自己差，咁實死啦"},{"pid":"d8055273152471feee8e3d86987ad5ffacb00aa5","tid":587984,"uid":13946,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T03:59:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f894cf1db5934b9735507a50f3d8496a44736703","tid":587984,"uid":137361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T04:00:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"76e6568147ee5bfa14c3797232715cd3339b3d8a","tid":587984,"uid":67976,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T04:15:58.000Z","msg":"喂都咁大個人啦 仲未識分人地對你有無野？<br />\n<br />\n根本上好多時人地點對你你自己會feel到<br />\n你地連出街都未出過就話想一齊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 會唔會skip左太多步驟<br />\n<br />\n細個或者會好似你咁諗 搏左先算 但你咁樣同搏佢撞邪鍾意你既機會率係一樣"},{"pid":"b69c6f2cdb6aee2929d650e5b2d31f5254ad2675","tid":587984,"uid":152714,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"1d62e093b9df70f3df7b0497e8d21b4b2a9ee88e","tid":587984,"uid":55897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T03:55:53.000Z","msg":"衰在要辭職...講真"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T04:17:02.000Z","msg":"唔洗辭職嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我諗住係得我哋兩個人嘅時候講<br />\n例如 搭lift嗰時 <br />\n<br />\n自己知 當事人知 咪算 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過其實我都想轉工 最近係因為佢 <br />\n我先至無揾工啫<br />\n<br />\n其實我一直都在改善自己 <br />\n不過我做慢咗 佢好似嚟早咗咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b805af64ed2e239a22b47a2aeaa43fa52a14bc27","tid":587984,"uid":169676,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4f7234a876f8c8fa67e8c5d06735157ab8b3102b","tid":587984,"uid":30374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T03:52:40.000Z","msg":"重來都只有因為冇做而後悔<br />\n唔會因爲做咗而後悔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申：All i咗左仲要自己親手整禮物"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T04:24:19.000Z","msg":"唔做就後悔<br />\n做咗又後悔<br />\n係未都後悔<br />\n不如照做咗先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc66aee299fe834dec39ac6939cfb38cfbc3e35c","tid":587984,"uid":137361,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T04:28:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"09d2f03bcb35b0529061808063678d6d919ebe18","tid":587984,"uid":22624,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"6629d46935fe242f06342117e0e5bb91f24f11c9","tid":587984,"uid":152714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"62128cabc41a2cd38c59b91a1e7baa246b2db1e3","tid":587984,"uid":78971,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ce2c6359f7752beb94f2cb468fb9987e7005cded","tid":587984,"uid":152714,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T03:10:43.000Z","msg":"我自己覺得大家成年人  廿幾歲 <br />\n應該識handle <br />\n<br />\n我表白啫 又唔係想做啲嘜<br />\n但只係想你知道我心意<br />\n啱嘅  咪大家可以行前一步<br />\n唔啱嘅  咪以後淨係做嘢囉 <br />\n加上我本身都忙 日頭工作 夜晚讀書 <br />\n只不過我年紀唔細 遇到啱嘅人 唔想錯過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n加上 大家雖然係同事 <br />\n不過可以話係唔同department 佢係隔離office<br />\n唔係朝見晚見嗰種"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T03:18:10.000Z","msg":"係成年人嘅就諗下人哋感受啦<br />\n你話「唔得嘅，咪以後淨係做野囉」<br />\n你得唔得先？<br />\n真係絲毫尷尬都唔會？<br />\n你做到咁人哋呢？<br />\n如果你自己都覺得機會微嘅，不如做住朋友了解多啲先啦，咁先係負責任嘅表現"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T03:30:01.000Z","msg":"其實我就係諗呢個問題<br />\n<br />\n但係如果淨係講自己 <br />\n我覺得自己可以放得低<br />\n佢就唔知做唔做到<br />\n<br />\n唉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔通 <br />\n真係應該慢慢走入人哋圈子 <br />\n慢慢刷好感度？<br />\n<br />\n但係男人老狗 係咁約女仔去行街睇戲食飯<br />\n目的好明顯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T04:46:15.000Z","msg":"約女仔行街睇戲食飯明顯，表白就唔明顯 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20f1637857b3d6de45efc80e4bd1b4d9b3be2a13","tid":587984,"uid":78234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T05:24:55.000Z","msg":"一樣鍾意左個女同事<br />\n但真係驚表白完佢會尷尬<br />\n我男人老狗臉皮厚就話姐,唔想搞到佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b77a7df5b326d6c083dc86d76ae10f59a06244b","tid":587984,"uid":153311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"20f1637857b3d6de45efc80e4bd1b4d9b3be2a13","tid":587984,"uid"